  "detailed_description": "<h1>Buzz</h1><p>English translation is not complete at this moment.The game has a lot of text in it, we are changing a lot of text during development, so english translation might not be up to date. Fortunately, The game development will completed very soon, so we will make english version ready as soon as game is completed.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><u>Speed is not only for racing but also for life.</u><br><br>The story begins:<br>In 2025,  the world economy collapsed. Government was no more authority. People lived in darkness, and jason were fallen into a trap. Will he make it trough, will he discovery the truth behind? What will he encounter?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What you will experience:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">High Speed </h2>Let Speed stimulate your adrenaline<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/693960/extras/\u6c2e\u6c14\u8d85\u8f66.gif?t=1554277813\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Road rage</h2>Provoke cars, fierce chase, are just the beginning to life as Jason.<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/693960/extras/\u8ffd\u9010.gif?t=1554277813\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Collecting</h2>You can get different motorcycle and a variety of equipment and select different way to complete tasks.<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/693960/extras/\u6548\u679c\u56fe2.jpg?t=1554277813\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Equipment</h2>Use powerful equipment to eliminate enemies<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/693960/extras/\u6548\u679c\u56fe4.jpg?t=1554277813\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Survival</h2>To survive the most important things are maintenance of the your machinery and yourself.<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/693960/extras/\u6548\u679c\u56fe5.jpg?t=1554277813\" ><br><br><br>Freely explored different beautiful landscape, ride a unleased horse. <br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/693960/extras/yellowstone_jump1.gif?t=1554277813\" ><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/693960/extras/\u8d8a\u91ce-\u9ad8\u98de.gif?t=1554277813\" ><br><br>Tons of various items crafting in the garage some of them is critical for some quest.<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/693960/extras/\u6361\u5783\u573e.gif?t=1554277813\" ><br><br>Things are always go out of your control<br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/693960/extras/\u8b66\u8f66\u6284\u5bb6.gif?t=1554277813\" >",
